title: Prinz Myshkin Garden
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Organic, Beer/Wine, European, German
description: Opened 2014, this newer Prinz Myshkin provides balanced vegetarian and vegan cuisine with natural and seasonal ingredients focusing on a rich taste. It's a two storey restaurant with a rooftop terrace and a garden, close to Nymphenburg castle. Offers a wide variety of food from snacks, salads, sandwiches, full menus, desserts. Vegan wine and drinks available.
